                            Convert crop residues into nutrient-rich compost through controlled decomposition.
                            This sustainable method transforms agricultural waste into valuable organic
                            fertilizer.
                        </p>

                        <div class="mb-6">
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Key Benefits:</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-1" id="ul-bullet">
                                <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
                                    <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    Reduces landfill waste
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
                                    <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    Creates natural fertilizer
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
                                    <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    Improves soil health
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
                                    <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    Cost-effective solution
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

